---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="openclaw → claude code" description="The middleware was the problem the entire time">
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-faint mb-4 animate-fade-up">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">writing</a> <span class="text-faint">/</span> openclaw → claude code
    </div>

    <article class="space-y-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-normal animate-fade-up delay-1">openclaw → claude code</h1>

      <div class="text-lg leading-loose space-y-4 animate-fade-up delay-2">
        <p>spent 12 hours deploying openclaw on a vps</p>

        <p>the bot couldn't read links<br />
        couldn't run commands without being asked twice<br />
        killed the conversation when i pushed back on its guardrails</p>

        <p>then i installed claude code on the same box<br />
        wrote a 200-line telegram bot<br />
        pasted my persona as CLAUDE.md</p>

        <p>1 hour. full tool access. uncut persona. opus brain.</p>

        <p><strong>the middleware was the problem the entire time.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border animate-fade-up delay-3">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">← back to writing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
